}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "7016A0373000" and "RoHS" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
The FCC test report says this FCC ID also covers the Sitecom WL-361 v1 001.
Per the manual, the default SSID is '''EnGeniusXXXXXX''' where '''XXXXXX''' is the last three octets of the wireless interface MAC address.
